SUMMARY:COX ASSET MEXICO SA DE C V — Virtual Fixed Income Investor Call
DESCRIPTION:Reach out to your dealer to confirm timing and availability\n\n
 Series of virtual fixed income investor calls. Deutsche Bank Securities co
 ordinating logistics.\nIssuer: COX ASSET MEXICO SA DE C V\nRoadshow: URL: 
 https://dealroadshow.com | Entry Code: COX2026 | Direct Link: https://deal
 roadshow.com/e/COX2026\n\nDeal context:\nCox Asset Mexico\, SA de CV — a s
 pecial purpose vehicle created by Cox ABG Group\, SA to acquire Iberdrola 
 México\, SA de CV — has mandated Barclays\, Citigroup\, Deutsche Bank Secu
 rities\, and Goldman Sachs as Global Coordinators and Joint Bookrunners\, 
 alongside BBVA\, Santander\, and Scotiabank as Joint Bookrunners\, for a d
 ual-tranche USD-denominated 144A/Reg S Senior Secured Notes offering. The 
 deal is expected to consist of a long 5-year and a 10-year benchmark-sized
  tranche with expected ratings of BBB- (Fitch) and Ba1 (Moody's)\, with in
 vestor calls commencing Tuesday\, April 28\, 2026\, subject to market cond
 itions. This is an acquisition financing SPV deal with a split rating stra
 ddling the IG/HY boundary.
